name: Gronsky's

”Alexa, ask gron skis What is Gronskys?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: gron skis
des:
The Gronsky's Alexa skill tells you information about Gronsky's Milk House located in High Bridge, NJ. It will also tell you the restaurant's current pancake of the month.

For more information about Gronsky's Milk House, visit its website at http://www.gronskys.com/
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
